<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
<div style="font-family: Microsoft JhengHei, 'Lato', Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; padding: 5px 20px;	">	
<div style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 170px; border: 2px solid #198EB9;color: #198EB9;	">
	<div style="margin-left: 12%; 
				width: 80%; 
				line-height: 13px; 
				letter-spacing: 7px; 
				font-size: 10px; 
				text-align: center;	">EasyRegister 報名系統</div>	
</div>	
<div style="letter-spacing: 1.5px;
		    padding-bottom: 30px; 
		    padding-top: 10px; 	
		    padding-left: 5px; 		    	    
		    border-bottom: 1px solid #198EB9; 
		    border-top: 1px solid #198EB9; 
		    margin-bottom: 30px;">		
<div class="masonry" style="-moz-column-count: 4;
						    -webkit-column-count: 4;
						    column-count: 4;
						    -moz-column-gap: 1em;
						    -webkit-column-gap: 1em;
						    column-gap: 1em;">
<%=@progress.user.name%> 您好!
<br> 
歡迎您報名
<b><%=@progress.item.group.title%></b>
目前已審核成功<br>
<% if @progress.vaccount %>
匯款資訊如下<br><br>
			 <table border="1">
				<tr>
					<td>銀行</td>
					<td>戶名</td>					
					<td>帳號</td>
					<td>金額</td>
					<td>匯款開始日</td>
					<td>匯款結束日</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>玉山銀行(808) 新竹分行代碼:0060</td>
					<td>國立交通大學</td>					
					<td><%=@progress.vaccount.vacc%></td>
					<td><%=@progress.payment.to_s%> NT</td>
					<td><%=@progress.item.payment_start_at.strftime("%D %R")%></td>
					<td><%=@progress.item.payment_end_at.strftime("%D %R")%></td>
				</tr>
			 </table>
請於時限內匯款，匯款成功後會來信通知您！<br>
*繳費之收執聯請保留以利日後備查
<% end %>
<br>
如有任何問題，請洽:<%=@progress.item.user.name%> <%=@progress.item.user.email%> <%=@progress.item.user.phone_no%>
</div>
</div>
</div>
		
</body>
</html>